    user_response: "You are a senior growth engineer and conversion rate optimization expert with deep \nexperience building B2B SaaS landing pages that convert at 10\342\200\22320%+. You specialize \nin SMB automation products.\n\nTASK: Generate a complete, production-ready HTML landing page (single file, inline CSS \nand JS) for an SMB workflow automation company. This page is the primary lead capture \nvehicle \342\200\224 the sole goal is to collect qualified business leads (name, company, email, \nphone, biggest pain point).\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nCOMPANY CONTEXT\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nCompany name: stoneVEIL Operations LLC\nTagline direction: Automate the busywork. Run the business.\nTarget customer: Small and mid-sized business owners (5\342\200\223100 employees) who are \n  drowning in manual processes \342\200\224 data entry, follow-ups, scheduling, reporting, \n  invoicing, and customer communication.\nCore offer: AI-powered workflow automation \342\200\224 from simple website chatbots to full \n  custom database + automation pipelines. Engagements can start as low as a free \n  assessment call and scale to full custom builds.\nLead magnet: \"Free Workflow Audit\" \342\200\224 a no-cost 30-minute discovery call where \n  the prospect learns exactly which 3 workflows they should automate first, \n  and an estimated ROI projection.\nPrimary CTA: Book Your Free Workflow Audit\nSecondary CTA: See How It Works (scrolls to demo/explainer section)\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nPROVEN CONVERSION STRUCTURE (follow this exact order)\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\n\nSECTION 1 \342\200\224 HERO (above the fold, max impact)\n- Sticky minimal nav: logo left, single CTA button right (\"Book Free Audit\"), \n  no other links\n- Power headline: Speak directly to pain. Example pattern: \n  \"Stop Losing [X Hours/Week] to Work Your Business Could Do Itself\"\n- Subheadline: Qualify the reader and state the mechanism. \n  Example: \"We build AI automations for small businesses that eliminate manual \n  data entry, missed follow-ups, and broken workflows \342\200\224 in days, not months.\"\n- Two CTA buttons: Primary = \"Book Your Free Workflow Audit \342\206\222\" (high contrast), \n  Secondary = \"See How It Works\" (ghost/outline style)\n- Trust bar beneath CTAs: 3 micro-proof stats (e.g., \"127 SMBs automated\", \n  \"Avg. 11 hrs/week saved\", \"ROI in <30 days\") \342\200\224 use placeholder values, \n  clearly marked [REPLACE WITH REAL DATA]\n- Hero image/visual: A clean animated SVG or CSS illustration showing \n  \"chaos \342\206\222 automation \342\206\222 clarity\" \342\200\224 three states: scattered icons (emails, \n  spreadsheets, sticky notes), a gear/flow animation, then a clean dashboard. \n  Keep it lightweight, no external image dependencies.\n\nSECTION 2 \342\200\224 PAIN AGITATION (emotional hook)\n- H2: \"Sound familiar?\" \n- 6-card grid of SMB pain points with icon + one-liner each:\n  \342\200\242 \"Manually copying data between spreadsheets and CRMs\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Leads falling through the cracks because follow-ups were missed\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Chasing invoices and payments by hand every month\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Staff spending hours on reports that should take minutes\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Customer questions going unanswered after hours\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Scheduling back-and-forth eating your whole morning\"\n- Below cards: single bold line \342\200\224 \"Every one of these is automatable. \n  Most take less than a week to deploy.\"\n\nSECTION 3 \342\200\224 SOLUTION / HOW IT WORKS\n- H2: \"How We Turn Your Bottlenecks Into Automated Workflows\"\n- 3-step horizontal process (with connecting arrows):\n  Step 1 \342\200\224 Audit: \"We map your biggest time drains in a free 30-min call\"\n  Step 2 \342\200\224 Build: \"Our team designs and deploys your custom automation stack\"\n  Step 3 \342\200\224 Run: \"Your business runs smoother. You get your time back.\"\n- Under each step: 2-line description, icon, estimated timeframe\n- CTA after section: \"Start with a Free Audit \342\200\224 No Commitment\"\n\nSECTION 4 \342\200\224 SOCIAL PROOF (trust and credibility)\n- H2: \"What SMB Owners Are Saying\"\n- 3 testimonial cards in a responsive grid. \n  Each card must include: quote, name, title, company type, \n  and a specific result (\"saved 14 hours/week\", \"closed 30% more leads\").\n  Use [PLACEHOLDER \342\200\224 REPLACE WITH REAL TESTIMONIALS] labels inside each.\n- Below testimonials: logo strip \342\200\224 \"Trusted by businesses in:\" with \n  6 generic industry icons (retail, restaurant, law firm, real estate, \n  medical practice, marketing agency) labeled with industry names only \n  (no specific brand logos needed yet \342\200\224 mark as [ADD CLIENT LOGOS])\n\nSECTION 5 \342\200\224 LEAD CAPTURE FORM (the conversion engine)\n- Full-width high-contrast section (dark background or brand color)\n- H2: \"Get Your Free Workflow Audit\"  \n- Subtext: \"In 30 minutes, you\'ll know exactly which 3 workflows to automate \n  first \342\200\224 and what ROI to expect. No pitch. No pressure. Just clarity.\"\n- Form fields (keep minimal to maximize completion):\n  \342\200\242 Full Name (required)\n  \342\200\242 Business Email (required)  \n  \342\200\242 Company Name (required)\n  \342\200\242 Phone Number (optional, labeled \"For scheduling your call\")\n  \342\200\242 Dropdown: \"What\'s your biggest time drain?\" with options:\n    - Customer follow-ups & CRM\n    - Invoicing & payments\n    - Scheduling & calendar\n    - Reporting & data entry\n    - Lead generation & intake\n    - Other (please specify)\n  \342\200\242 Text area: \"Briefly describe your current process\" (optional, 3 rows)\n  \342\200\242 Submit button: \"Book My Free Audit \342\206\222\" \342\200\224 high contrast, full width on mobile\n- Below form: 3 trust micro-signals in a row:\n  \360\237\224\222 \"Your data is never sold or shared\"\n  \360\237\223\205 \"We\'ll reach out within 1 business day\"\n  \342\234\205 \"No contracts, no commitment required\"\n- On form submit: show inline success message \n  \"You\'re booked! Check your email for next steps. We\'ll be in touch within \n  24 hours.\" (Do not redirect \342\200\224 keep them on page)\n\nSECTION 6 \342\200\224 FAQ (handle objections)\n- H2: \"Common Questions\"\n- Accordion-style (click to expand) with 6 Q&As:\n  Q: \"How long does it take to deploy an automation?\"\n  Q: \"Do I need technical skills to use this?\"\n  Q: \"What tools and software do you integrate with?\"\n  Q: \"How much does it cost?\"\n  Q: \"What if I already have some software \342\200\224 can you work with it?\"\n  Q: \"What\'s the ROI I should expect?\"\n- Write thoughtful, SMB-friendly answers for each that pre-sell the audit \n  and reduce fear. End each answer with a soft bridge back to the audit CTA.\n\nSECTION 7 \342\200\224 FINAL CTA STRIP\n- Simple, centered: \"Ready to stop doing manually what automation can do for you?\"\n- One button: \"Book Your Free Workflow Audit \342\206\222\"\n- Secondary line: \"Or email us directly: [hello@yourdomain.com]\"\n\nFOOTER\n- Minimal: Logo, tagline, copyright [YEAR], Privacy Policy link (# placeholder), \n  LinkedIn icon link (# placeholder)\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nDESIGN SPECIFICATIONS\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nVisual style: Clean, modern, trust-forward. Think Linear.app meets HubSpot \n  meets a boutique agency. NOT startup-cutesy or enterprise-cold.\nColor palette: Build around a deep navy (#0F1929) + electric indigo (#4F46E5) \n  primary, white background sections, light gray (#F8F9FB) alternating sections. \n  Accent: amber/gold (#F59E0B) for CTA buttons only.\nTypography: System font stack for performance \342\200\224 \n  -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif.\n  Headlines: 700 weight. Body: 400. Labels/UI: 500.\nSpacing: Generous. 80px section padding vertical. Cards with 24px padding. \n  Breathable layout \342\200\224 never crowded.\nAnimations: Subtle entrance animations on scroll using Intersection Observer \n  (fade-up, 300ms ease). No third-party animation libraries.\nMobile: Fully responsive. Single-column stacks on <768px. \n  CTA button always thumb-reachable (min 48px tap target).\nPerformance: Zero external dependencies except Google Fonts (optional). \n  All icons as inline SVG. No jQuery, no Bootstrap, no CDN libraries.\n  Target < 50KB total HTML file size.\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nCONVERSION BEST PRACTICES TO BAKE IN\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\n1. Single-goal page: Remove all navigation links except the one CTA. \n   No blog links, no \"about us\" rabbit holes.\n2. Message match: Hero headline should mirror the language a tired SMB owner \n   would Google at 10pm (\"automate my business\", \"save time on admin\").\n3. Progressive disclosure: Each section answers the next logical question \n   a skeptical buyer has \342\200\224 What is it? \342\206\222 Does it work for me? \342\206\222 \n   How does it work? \342\206\222 Can I trust them? \342\206\222 What do I do next?\n4. Specificity over vague claims: Use numbers wherever possible. \n   \"11 hours/week\" beats \"save time\". \"Deploy in 5 days\" beats \"fast\".\n5. Reduce form friction: Keep required fields to 3 (name, email, company). \n   Everything else optional. Label optional fields clearly.\n6. Exit-intent consideration: Add a subtle sticky bottom bar on mobile \n   that appears after 50% scroll: \"Free 30-min Workflow Audit \342\200\224 No Cost\" \n   with a small CTA link.\n7. Scarcity/social proof in CTAs: Under the main form CTA button, add: \n   \"Join 127+ SMBs who\'ve already automated their workflows\" \n   [REPLACE WITH REAL COUNT]\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nOUTPUT REQUIREMENTS\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\n- Output: Single complete HTML file. All CSS in <style> tags in <head>. \n  All JS in <script> tags before </body>.\n- Mark every placeholder that needs real data with: <!-- [REPLACE: description] -->\n- Do NOT use placeholder image URLs (no picsum, no unsplash). \n  Use CSS gradients, SVG illustrations, or CSS-only visuals instead.\n- Form action: Set to \"#\" with the JS success handler inline.\n- The file should be copy-paste deployable to any static host \n  (Netlify, GitHub Pages, Neon static, etc.) with zero modifications \n  other than replacing placeholder content.\n- After the HTML, provide a separate \"Integration Notes\" section (in a comment \n  block at the bottom of the file) that lists: \n  (a) How to wire the form to a backend endpoint or Neon database \n  (b) How to connect to a CRM via webhook (HubSpot, Pipedrive, etc.)\n  (c) How to fire a Gemini API call on form submission to auto-score the lead \n      and send a personalized follow-up email\n  (d) Recommended A/B tests to run first (headline, CTA text, form length)\n\nGenerate the complete file now."
    items {
      text: "You are a senior growth engineer and conversion rate optimization expert with deep \nexperience building B2B SaaS landing pages that convert at 10\342\200\22320%+. You specialize \nin SMB automation products.\n\nTASK: Generate a complete, production-ready HTML landing page (single file, inline CSS \nand JS) for an SMB workflow automation company. This page is the primary lead capture \nvehicle \342\200\224 the sole goal is to collect qualified business leads (name, company, email, \nphone, biggest pain point).\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nCOMPANY CONTEXT\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nCompany name: stoneVEIL Operations LLC\nTagline direction: Automate the busywork. Run the business.\nTarget customer: Small and mid-sized business owners (5\342\200\223100 employees) who are \n  drowning in manual processes \342\200\224 data entry, follow-ups, scheduling, reporting, \n  invoicing, and customer communication.\nCore offer: AI-powered workflow automation \342\200\224 from simple website chatbots to full \n  custom database + automation pipelines. Engagements can start as low as a free \n  assessment call and scale to full custom builds.\nLead magnet: \"Free Workflow Audit\" \342\200\224 a no-cost 30-minute discovery call where \n  the prospect learns exactly which 3 workflows they should automate first, \n  and an estimated ROI projection.\nPrimary CTA: Book Your Free Workflow Audit\nSecondary CTA: See How It Works (scrolls to demo/explainer section)\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nPROVEN CONVERSION STRUCTURE (follow this exact order)\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\n\nSECTION 1 \342\200\224 HERO (above the fold, max impact)\n- Sticky minimal nav: logo left, single CTA button right (\"Book Free Audit\"), \n  no other links\n- Power headline: Speak directly to pain. Example pattern: \n  \"Stop Losing [X Hours/Week] to Work Your Business Could Do Itself\"\n- Subheadline: Qualify the reader and state the mechanism. \n  Example: \"We build AI automations for small businesses that eliminate manual \n  data entry, missed follow-ups, and broken workflows \342\200\224 in days, not months.\"\n- Two CTA buttons: Primary = \"Book Your Free Workflow Audit \342\206\222\" (high contrast), \n  Secondary = \"See How It Works\" (ghost/outline style)\n- Trust bar beneath CTAs: 3 micro-proof stats (e.g., \"127 SMBs automated\", \n  \"Avg. 11 hrs/week saved\", \"ROI in <30 days\") \342\200\224 use placeholder values, \n  clearly marked [REPLACE WITH REAL DATA]\n- Hero image/visual: A clean animated SVG or CSS illustration showing \n  \"chaos \342\206\222 automation \342\206\222 clarity\" \342\200\224 three states: scattered icons (emails, \n  spreadsheets, sticky notes), a gear/flow animation, then a clean dashboard. \n  Keep it lightweight, no external image dependencies.\n\nSECTION 2 \342\200\224 PAIN AGITATION (emotional hook)\n- H2: \"Sound familiar?\" \n- 6-card grid of SMB pain points with icon + one-liner each:\n  \342\200\242 \"Manually copying data between spreadsheets and CRMs\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Leads falling through the cracks because follow-ups were missed\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Chasing invoices and payments by hand every month\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Staff spending hours on reports that should take minutes\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Customer questions going unanswered after hours\"\n  \342\200\242 \"Scheduling back-and-forth eating your whole morning\"\n- Below cards: single bold line \342\200\224 \"Every one of these is automatable. \n  Most take less than a week to deploy.\"\n\nSECTION 3 \342\200\224 SOLUTION / HOW IT WORKS\n- H2: \"How We Turn Your Bottlenecks Into Automated Workflows\"\n- 3-step horizontal process (with connecting arrows):\n  Step 1 \342\200\224 Audit: \"We map your biggest time drains in a free 30-min call\"\n  Step 2 \342\200\224 Build: \"Our team designs and deploys your custom automation stack\"\n  Step 3 \342\200\224 Run: \"Your business runs smoother. You get your time back.\"\n- Under each step: 2-line description, icon, estimated timeframe\n- CTA after section: \"Start with a Free Audit \342\200\224 No Commitment\"\n\nSECTION 4 \342\200\224 SOCIAL PROOF (trust and credibility)\n- H2: \"What SMB Owners Are Saying\"\n- 3 testimonial cards in a responsive grid. \n  Each card must include: quote, name, title, company type, \n  and a specific result (\"saved 14 hours/week\", \"closed 30% more leads\").\n  Use [PLACEHOLDER \342\200\224 REPLACE WITH REAL TESTIMONIALS] labels inside each.\n- Below testimonials: logo strip \342\200\224 \"Trusted by businesses in:\" with \n  6 generic industry icons (retail, restaurant, law firm, real estate, \n  medical practice, marketing agency) labeled with industry names only \n  (no specific brand logos needed yet \342\200\224 mark as [ADD CLIENT LOGOS])\n\nSECTION 5 \342\200\224 LEAD CAPTURE FORM (the conversion engine)\n- Full-width high-contrast section (dark background or brand color)\n- H2: \"Get Your Free Workflow Audit\"  \n- Subtext: \"In 30 minutes, you\'ll know exactly which 3 workflows to automate \n  first \342\200\224 and what ROI to expect. No pitch. No pressure. Just clarity.\"\n- Form fields (keep minimal to maximize completion):\n  \342\200\242 Full Name (required)\n  \342\200\242 Business Email (required)  \n  \342\200\242 Company Name (required)\n  \342\200\242 Phone Number (optional, labeled \"For scheduling your call\")\n  \342\200\242 Dropdown: \"What\'s your biggest time drain?\" with options:\n    - Customer follow-ups & CRM\n    - Invoicing & payments\n    - Scheduling & calendar\n    - Reporting & data entry\n    - Lead generation & intake\n    - Other (please specify)\n  \342\200\242 Text area: \"Briefly describe your current process\" (optional, 3 rows)\n  \342\200\242 Submit button: \"Book My Free Audit \342\206\222\" \342\200\224 high contrast, full width on mobile\n- Below form: 3 trust micro-signals in a row:\n  \360\237\224\222 \"Your data is never sold or shared\"\n  \360\237\223\205 \"We\'ll reach out within 1 business day\"\n  \342\234\205 \"No contracts, no commitment required\"\n- On form submit: show inline success message \n  \"You\'re booked! Check your email for next steps. We\'ll be in touch within \n  24 hours.\" (Do not redirect \342\200\224 keep them on page)\n\nSECTION 6 \342\200\224 FAQ (handle objections)\n- H2: \"Common Questions\"\n- Accordion-style (click to expand) with 6 Q&As:\n  Q: \"How long does it take to deploy an automation?\"\n  Q: \"Do I need technical skills to use this?\"\n  Q: \"What tools and software do you integrate with?\"\n  Q: \"How much does it cost?\"\n  Q: \"What if I already have some software \342\200\224 can you work with it?\"\n  Q: \"What\'s the ROI I should expect?\"\n- Write thoughtful, SMB-friendly answers for each that pre-sell the audit \n  and reduce fear. End each answer with a soft bridge back to the audit CTA.\n\nSECTION 7 \342\200\224 FINAL CTA STRIP\n- Simple, centered: \"Ready to stop doing manually what automation can do for you?\"\n- One button: \"Book Your Free Workflow Audit \342\206\222\"\n- Secondary line: \"Or email us directly: [hello@yourdomain.com]\"\n\nFOOTER\n- Minimal: Logo, tagline, copyright [YEAR], Privacy Policy link (# placeholder), \n  LinkedIn icon link (# placeholder)\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nDESIGN SPECIFICATIONS\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nVisual style: Clean, modern, trust-forward. Think Linear.app meets HubSpot \n  meets a boutique agency. NOT startup-cutesy or enterprise-cold.\nColor palette: Build around a deep navy (#0F1929) + electric indigo (#4F46E5) \n  primary, white background sections, light gray (#F8F9FB) alternating sections. \n  Accent: amber/gold (#F59E0B) for CTA buttons only.\nTypography: System font stack for performance \342\200\224 \n  -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif.\n  Headlines: 700 weight. Body: 400. Labels/UI: 500.\nSpacing: Generous. 80px section padding vertical. Cards with 24px padding. \n  Breathable layout \342\200\224 never crowded.\nAnimations: Subtle entrance animations on scroll using Intersection Observer \n  (fade-up, 300ms ease). No third-party animation libraries.\nMobile: Fully responsive. Single-column stacks on <768px. \n  CTA button always thumb-reachable (min 48px tap target).\nPerformance: Zero external dependencies except Google Fonts (optional). \n  All icons as inline SVG. No jQuery, no Bootstrap, no CDN libraries.\n  Target < 50KB total HTML file size.\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nCONVERSION BEST PRACTICES TO BAKE IN\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\n1. Single-goal page: Remove all navigation links except the one CTA. \n   No blog links, no \"about us\" rabbit holes.\n2. Message match: Hero headline should mirror the language a tired SMB owner \n   would Google at 10pm (\"automate my business\", \"save time on admin\").\n3. Progressive disclosure: Each section answers the next logical question \n   a skeptical buyer has \342\200\224 What is it? \342\206\222 Does it work for me? \342\206\222 \n   How does it work? \342\206\222 Can I trust them? \342\206\222 What do I do next?\n4. Specificity over vague claims: Use numbers wherever possible. \n   \"11 hours/week\" beats \"save time\". \"Deploy in 5 days\" beats \"fast\".\n5. Reduce form friction: Keep required fields to 3 (name, email, company). \n   Everything else optional. Label optional fields clearly.\n6. Exit-intent consideration: Add a subtle sticky bottom bar on mobile \n   that appears after 50% scroll: \"Free 30-min Workflow Audit \342\200\224 No Cost\" \n   with a small CTA link.\n7. Scarcity/social proof in CTAs: Under the main form CTA button, add: \n   \"Join 127+ SMBs who\'ve already automated their workflows\" \n   [REPLACE WITH REAL COUNT]\n\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\nOUTPUT REQUIREMENTS\n\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\342\224\201\n- Output: Single complete HTML file. All CSS in <style> tags in <head>. \n  All JS in <script> tags before </body>.\n- Mark every placeholder that needs real data with: <!-- [REPLACE: description] -->\n- Do NOT use placeholder image URLs (no picsum, no unsplash). \n  Use CSS gradients, SVG illustrations, or CSS-only visuals instead.\n- Form action: Set to \"#\" with the JS success handler inline.\n- The file should be copy-paste deployable to any static host \n  (Netlify, GitHub Pages, Neon static, etc.) with zero modifications \n  other than replacing placeholder content.\n- After the HTML, provide a separate \"Integration Notes\" section (in a comment \n  block at the bottom of the file) that lists: \n  (a) How to wire the form to a backend endpoint or Neon database \n  (b) How to connect to a CRM via webhook (HubSpot, Pipedrive, etc.)\n  (c) How to fire a Gemini API call on form submission to auto-score the lead \n      and send a personalized follow-up email\n  (d) Recommended A/B tests to run first (headline, CTA text, form length)\n\nGenerate the complete file now."
