          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  <section class=\"py-24 px-6 bg-white\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center space-y-16\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      "
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      <!-- FAQ H2 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl space-y-4\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-navy\">Common Questions</h2>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600\">Addressing common objections and clarifying the operational scope of stoneVEIL automations.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      <!-- Accordion Grid -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      <div class=\"w-full space-y-4\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        "
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Accordion Question 1 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"border border-slate-150 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <button class=\"w-full py-5 px-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-none focus:bg-slate-50 transition-colors font-display font-bold text-brand-navy leading-snug md:text-lg\" onclick=\"toggleAccordion(this)\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span>How long does it take to deploy an automation?</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span class=\"text-brand-indigo font-bold transform transition-transform duration-200 text-xl ml-4 shrink-0\">&plus;</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </button>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"accordion-content bg-slate-50/50\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"p-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Simple integrations\342\200\224such as linking Web Forms straight to HubSpot CRM, building Slack triggers, or custom customer onboarding dispatches\342\200\224can go live in <strong>3 to 5 business days</strong>.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Complete multi-app systems with AI database scoring might require 2 weeks of engineering. We coordinate everything in your audit session first. <a href=\"#audit-form-section\" class=\"text-brand-indigo font-medium hover:underline\">Start with an audit &rarr;</a></p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Accordion Question 2 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"border border-slate-150 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <button class=\"w-full py-5 px-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-none focus:bg-slate-50 transition-colors font-display font-bold text-brand-navy leading-snug md:text-lg\" onclick=\"toggleAccordion(this)\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span>Do I need technical skills to use this?</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span class=\"text-brand-indigo font-bold transform transition-transform duration-200 text-xl ml-4 shrink-0\">&plus;</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </button>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"accordion-content bg-slate-50/50\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"p-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p><strong>Absolutely not.</strong> We design every automation to run completely hands-free in the background. If manual intervention is needed (like reviewing an AI draft before it publishes), we provide a super-simple, humdrum dashboard with clean, literal buttons.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>We write and maintain all code on the backend, making usage dead-simple for you and your crew. <a href=\"#audit-form-section\" class=\"text-brand-indigo font-medium hover:underline\">Learn more in your free call &rarr;</a></p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Accordion Question 3 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"border border-slate-150 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <button class=\"w-full py-5 px-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-none focus:bg-slate-50 transition-colors font-display font-bold text-brand-navy leading-snug md:text-lg\" onclick=\"toggleAccordion(this)\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span>What tools and software do you integrate with?</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span class=\"text-brand-indigo font-bold transform transition-transform duration-200 text-xl ml-4 shrink-0\">&plus;</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </button>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"accordion-content bg-slate-50/50\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"p-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>We integrate with virtually anything that has an API. This includes CRM systems (HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive), messaging protocols (Slack, WhatsApp, Gmail, Twilio), databases (Airtable, SQL, Google Sheets), and standard billing stacks (Stripe, QuickBooks, Xero).</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>If your tooling is completely legacy, we can build custom micro-scripts to scrape or push data efficiently. <a href=\"#audit-form-section\" class=\"text-brand-indigo font-medium hover:underline\">Check compatible tools &rarr;</a></p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Accordion Question 4 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"border border-slate-150 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <button class=\"w-full py-5 px-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-none focus:bg-slate-50 transition-colors font-display font-bold text-brand-navy leading-snug md:text-lg\" onclick=\"toggleAccordion(this)\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span>How much does it cost?</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span class=\"text-brand-indigo font-bold transform transition-transform duration-200 text-xl ml-4 shrink-0\">&plus;</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </button>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"accordion-content bg-slate-50/50\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"p-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>The discovery audit itself is completely <strong>0 USD</strong>. Practical custom, permanent automation creations scale according to system scopes (ranging from 1,200 USD setups for focused micro-pipelines up to recurring retainer plans for full boutique pipeline administration).</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Every single deploy is meticulously scoped with guaranteed savings parameters before you spend a single dime. <a href=\"#audit-form-section\" class=\"text-brand-indigo font-medium hover:underline\">Get an exact quote on your call &rarr;</a></p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Accordion Question 5 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"border border-slate-150 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <button class=\"w-full py-5 px-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-none focus:bg-slate-50 transition-colors font-display font-bold text-brand-navy leading-snug md:text-lg\" onclick=\"toggleAccordion(this)\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span>What if I already have some software \342\200\224 can you work with it?</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span class=\"text-brand-indigo font-bold transform transition-transform duration-200 text-xl ml-4 shrink-0\">&plus;</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </button>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"accordion-content bg-slate-50/50\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"p-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p><strong>Yes, we prefer it.</strong> Our engineers match and weave programmatic hooks directly inside your current workflow. Our absolute core purpose is to streamline what you have, never forcing you to purchase separate unneeded tools or migrate away from elements you like.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>We connect the loose strands to eliminate manual double-handling of data. <a href=\"#audit-form-section\" class=\"text-brand-indigo font-medium hover:underline\">Map your existing tools &rarr;</a></p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Accordion Question 6 -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"border border-slate-150 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <button class=\"w-full py-5 px-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-none focus:bg-slate-50 transition-colors font-display font-bold text-brand-navy leading-snug md:text-lg\" onclick=\"toggleAccordion(this)\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span>What\'s the ROI I should expect?</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <span class=\"text-brand-indigo font-bold transform transition-transform duration-200 text-xl ml-4 shrink-0\">&plus;</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </button>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"accordion-content bg-slate-50/50\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"p-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>On average, stoneVEIL customers recapture <strong>11 hours per week per employee</strong> from tedious entry, scheduling overhead, and CRM maintenance. For a small crew of 5, that\'s equivalent to 2,800 saved labor hours annually.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Most projects recoup their entire initialization costs within 30 days of implementation. <a href=\"#audit-form-section\" class=\"text-brand-indigo font-medium hover:underline\">Calculate your actual ROI with us &rarr;</a></p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "      </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
