  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Reviewing Server Implementation**\n\nI\'ve successfully created the initial landing page as a complete HTML file. Now, I\'m shifting focus to `server.ts`. The primary objective is to build a server that securely integrates with the Gemini `gemini-3.5-flash` model on the server-side. Specifically, I\'m working to expose an `/api/lead` endpoint.\n\n\n**Constructing Server Logic**\n\nI\'m now fully immersed in building the `server.ts` file. My goal is to orchestrate the lead scoring and workflow generation. I\'m focusing on the implementation details: handling the lead form inputs, interfacing with the Gemini model via the `@google/genai` SDK for custom workflow recommendations and outputting a high-value JSON payload to the client. I\'ve also verified the server\'s boilerplate including port, host, Vite integration, and SDK initialization. Now, I\'m checking the file tree before proceeding.\n\n\n"
